data.description: Ask about Assumable VA loan at 5%. RV parking! Split level home with large entry and wide staircases. Vaulted ceilings give the main floor a roomy open feel. Kitchen and dining area have lots of cabinet storage. Raw cut granite counter tops, pantry, & breakfast bar with gas range. Large South facing window in living room gives lots of light and warmth in the winter. The driveway also faces South to help with snow melt. Dining room has sliding door and back deck overlooks well landscaped yard. The main bedroom has a walk in closet, a bathroom with double sinks and granite counter tops and a jetted tub/shower. There is an additional bedroom and bath on the main floor. Walk out basement has its own private patio off the family room. FR is wired for TV. 2 additional egress bedroom and a 3/4 bath with large tiled shower. Storage under stairs turned into a child's playroom.
